OL,3,CLocals unite in bid to save historic
OL,4,Cpub
OL,6,FPeople in are trying to save a 170-
OL,7,Fyear-old pub from being turned into a
OL,8,Fhouse.JThe current owner of The Old
OL,9,FNeighbourhood on Chalford Hill has put
OL,10,Fin a planning application for it to be
OL,11,Ftransformed into a private home,
OL,12,Ffollowing what it called "a change in
OL,13,Fcustomer behaviour".
OL,15,FThe pub shut in September 2022 and
OL,16,Fresidents are striving to get it open
OL,17,Fagain.
