OL,6,FThe Chalford Hill Community Benefit
OL,7,FSociety has ramped up its campaign to
OL,8,Fbuy the pub and run it as a community
OL,9,Fhub.
OL,11,FSpeaking to ITV News West Country, Tim
OL,12,FWoodfine from the society, said: "The
OL,13,FChalford parish has quite a big
OL,14,Fpopulation and is larger than nearby
OL,15,Fpopulations such as Nailsworth that
OL,16,Fhave several pubs and restaurants."
OL,18,FDavid Parrott has been an active
OL,19,Fmember of the community for around
OL,20,Fsixty years.
