OL,6,F"It's a meeting place that kept us
OL,7,Fgoing through Covid. This was the
OL,8,Fshop, it was the hub, and we even had
OL,9,Fa little market that sprang up in the
OL,10,Fcar park."
OL,12,FEmma and her daughter Tabitha live
OL,13,Fnearby and told ITV News West Country
OL,14,Fthe pub holds special memories for
OL,15,Fthem.
