OL,6,F"A lot of the residents have worked
OL,7,Fhere. Especially with it being so out
OL,8,Fof the way, there are not a lot of
OL,9,Femployment opportunities for young
OL,10,Fpeople. Both of my children had said
OL,11,Fthey wanted to get a job there."
OL,13,FA change of use application was lodged
OL,14,Fwith Stroud District Council in March
OL,15,F2024, with a planning statement
OL,16,Fdetailing how the building was
OL,17,F"deteriorating".
