OL,4,Cpub
OL,6,FProperty consultant Bruton Knowles has
OL,7,Fsaid that continuing to operate the
OL,8,Fbuilding as a pub would be an unlikely
OL,9,Foutcome.
OL,11,FIt said: "We acknowledge the concerns
OL,12,Fof local residents when it comes to
OL,13,Fthe Old Neighbourhood Inn.
OL,15,F"However, the property's long-term
OL,16,Fviability as a business has been
OL,17,Freviewed and considered unlikely in
OL,18,Fthis current and difficult trading
OL,19,Fclimate.
